Liverpool lost 2-1 to Aston Villa in the FA Cup final at Wembley on Sunday . 
  Steven Gerrard will leave the club at the end of the season . 
  Kolo Toure admitted Gerrard was 'sad' after the loss but also felt sorry for the fans . 
  Brendan Rodgers became the first manager since the 1950s not to win a trophy in his first three years . 
 